div.div:
This diagram shows the execution of a selected backup in a thread. In addition, if business software is detected, it prevents the backup from starting or pauses it if it is in progress. Finally, we can interact with the backups by calling the backup job management function.
We see diagrams that form loops, which represent the different events that interact with the backup jobs.
